@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ohwucb(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs((0.24 + (v1 + 0.31 + v0 + 1.00)))
    v2 = ((wp.exp(v1 + 0.75) - (v0 + 0.55 / v1 + 0.36)) - 0.95)
    v0 = (wp.sin(wp.abs(v0 + 0.70)) / (v0 / (v2 + 0.31 * tmp + 0.85)))
    v0 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.34 * v0 + 0.32)) / (wp.exp(v2 + 0.36) * (v1 + 0.65 - v1 + 0.14)))
    data[tid] = v0
